channel.title: [PI] Starting Location
channel.description:
Alright so... I go into my Config.java and change the starting location but it will not change the actual starting area when I make a new account. I compile and everything. I also change the starting items when you make a new account and that won't work either, any ideas?
EDIT: I got the starting location to fix by going to Player.java, but the starter items won't change.
